## Troubleshooting Protocols

### Common Analytical Issues
| Issue | Possible Cause | Diagnostic | Solution |
|-------|----------------|------------|----------|
| Poor peak resolution | Column degradation | Retention time shift | Column replacement |
| Low sensitivity | Detector contamination | Signal-to-noise ratio | Detector maintenance |
| Mass spectral mismatch | Library error | Manual verification | Alternative identification |
| Inconsistent results | Sample degradation | Replicate analysis | Sample storage review |

### Common Attribution Issues
| Issue | Possible Cause | Diagnostic | Solution |
|-------|----------------|------------|----------|
| Ambiguous markers | Mixed routes | Marker analysis | Advanced profiling |
| Low impurity levels | Purification | Sensitivity check | Enhanced detection |
| Novel markers | New method | Literature review | Method development |

